file_content.text: Come on, come on.... Warden Graal? This is Captain Black, do you read me?
The key's gone. The Esh-kha took it. And they're imprisoned all over Belsavis.
You're breaking up, Captain. Stay where you are. I'll send a rescue party.
Do you read me? We're sitting on a hive of those things! Do you read me...? Blast!
You want a piece of me? Come and get it!
Captain, I'm losing you. Stay in your position. Rescue's en route.
The warden's indisposed. What's your status?
